name: Greek Mask Lamp 2 - On Off Switch
description:
Villa Kérylos Greek Mask Lamp 2/6

Click on the Greek Mask Lamp base to switch it on and off. 
Sync a Tezos Wallet and try to find the Rainbow switch for glory !
I'll Mint all the raw materials images used to make this piece so you can play and make you own Greek Mask Lamp.
If you do, I'll be very happy if you send me one piece of it.
